#. Tag: para
#: system_repair.xml:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have entered the rescue system, you can use the virtual consoles "
"that can be reached with <keycombo><keycap function=\"alt\"></"
"keycap><keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> to <keycombo><keycap function=\"alt"
"\"></keycap><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo>."
